snippet: For more than two weeks, a stench of feces, ammonium and laundry detergent wafted through the air in the southwestern corner of the continental United States. Residents who contacted government offices got no answers....

headline.main: Red Sox Say Price Will Not Need Arm Surgery or Injection
headline.print_headline: Red Sox Say Price Will Not Need Arm Surgery or Injection

lead_paragraph: For more than two weeks, a stench of feces, ammonium and laundry detergent wafted through the air in the southwestern corner of the continental United States. Residents who contacted government offices got no answers.
